-- Three big banks encourage discount window use
-- 
-- Wed Aug 22, 2007 1:07pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/22/us-banks-discount-idUSWNAS265520070822

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Bank of America Corp, JPMorgan Chase & Co and Wachovia Corp on Wednesday said they each borrowed $500 million at the discount window facility announced by the U.S. Federal Reserve last week. 

 Citigroup Inc made a similar announcement earlier Wednesday. (Reporting by Jonathan Stempel)